Originating from the deep, dense wild forests of Aravallis, Saffola Wild Forest Organic Honey is the result of nectar collected by bees from a wide range of rich wild floral species. Saffola Wild Forest Organic Honey is tested using the NMR (Nuclear Magnetic Resonance ) Test to ensure it is pure, free from added Sugar and free from adulteration. Organic Honey is collected from the pollen of organically grown plants, and it is a natural food that comes with tons of uses and benefits and should be used in its pure form. Pure Honey is also a healthy alternative to sugar and is considered one of the most wonderful gifts that nature has ever gifted to mankind. 
Saffola Wild Forest Organic Honey is natural honey in its purest form. It is tested and approved after many rigorous quality checks including the NMR test. Each bottle of Saffola Wild Forest Organic Honey contains natural antioxidants, has No Added Sugar and comes with a Purity certificate that is made available to its consumers.
